nodes.name: pmc
nodes.description: Announcement of a pre-market consultation. A pre-market consultation is not a call for competition and no procurement documents are available at the time of consultation. A consultation may or may not be followed by a future competition.

nodes.name: compl
nodes.description: Announcement of the completion of a contract.

nodes.name: can-standard
nodes.description: Announcement of the results of a call for competition concerning Contracts or Concessions.Not later than 30 days after the conclusion of a Contract or of a Framework Agreement, following the decision to award or conclude it, Contracting Authorities shall send a Contract Award Notice on the results of the Procurement Procedure. Such Notices shall contain the information set out in Annex V part D and shall be published in accordance with Article 51.

nodes.name: veat
nodes.description: Announcement of the intention to award of a Contract without prior publication of a Contract Notice in the Official Journal of the European Union.

nodes.name: cn-desg
nodes.description: Announcement of a call for competition concerning the acquisition, mainly in the fields of town and country planning, architecture and engineering or data processing, of a plan or design selected by a jury. Contracting Authorities that intend to carry out a design contest shall make known their intention by means of a Contest Notice. Where they intend to award a subsequent service Contract pursuant to Article 32(4), this shall be indicated in the Contest Notice. [Directive 2014/24/EU].

nodes.name: cn-social
nodes.description: Announcement of a call for competition concerning Contracts for social and other specific services.

nodes.name: cn-standard
nodes.description: Announcement of a call for competition concerning Contracts or Concessions. Contract Notices shall be used as a means of calling for Competition in respect of all Procedures, without prejudice to the second subparagraph of Article 26(5) and Article 32. Contract Notices shall contain the information set out in Annex V part C and shall be published in accordance with Article 51. [Directive 2014/24/EU].

nodes.name: pin-cfc-standard
nodes.description: Announcement of intentions of Planned Procurements used as a call for Competion.For Restricted Procedures and Competitive Procedures with negotiation, sub-central Contracting Authorities may use a Prior iinformation Notice as a call for competition pursuant to Article 26(5), [...]. [Directive 2014/24/EU].

nodes.name: pin-buyer
nodes.description: Announcement of intentions of Planned Procurements. Contracting Authorities may make known their intentions of Planned Procurements through the publication of a Prior Information Notice. Those Notices shall contain the information set out in Annex V part B section I. They shall be published either by the Publications Office of the European Union or by the Contracting Authorities on their Buyer profiles in accordance with point 2(b) of Annex VIII . Where the Prior Information Notice is published by the Contracting Authorities on their Buyer profile, they shall send a Notice of the publication on their Buyer profile to the Publications Office of the European Union in accordance with Annex VIII. Those Notices shall contain the information set out in Annex V part A. [Directive 2014/24/EU].

nodes.name: pin-rtl
nodes.description: Announcement of intentions of Planned Procurements in view of shortening time limits for reception of Tenders. Where contracting authorities have published a Prior Information Notice which was not itself used as a means of calling for Competition, the minimum time limit for the receipt of Tenders, as laid down in the second subparagraph of paragraph 1 of this Article, may be shortened to 15 days, [...].

nodes.name: pin-only
nodes.description: Announcement of intentions of Planned Procurements for information purposes. Contracting Authorities may make known their intentions of Planned Procurements through the publication of a Prior Information Notice. Those Notices shall contain the information set out in Annex V part B section I. They shall be published either by the Publications Office of the European Union or by the Contracting Authorities on their Buyer profiles in accordance with point 2(b) of Annex VIII . Where the Prior Information Notice is published by the Contracting Authorities on their Buyer profile, they shall send a Notice of the publication on their Buyer profile to the Publications Office of the European Union in accordance with Annex VIII. Those Notices shall contain the information set out in Annex V part A. [Directive 2014/24/EU].

nodes.name: qu-sy
nodes.description: Announcement of a System of qualification of Economic Operators on the basis of Exclusion and Selection Criteria. The announcement can be used as a call for Competition.When a call for Competition is made by means of a Notice on the existence of a qualification System, specific Contracts for the works, supplies or services covered by the qualification System shall be awarded by Restricted Procedures or Negotiated Procedures, in which all Tenderers and Participants are selected among the Candidates already qualified in accordance with such a System.

nodes.name: subco
nodes.description: Announcement of a call for Competition by successful Tenderers which are not Contracting Authorities/Entities concerning Contracts for social and other specific services.

nodes.name: can-desg
nodes.description: Announcement of the results of a call for competition concerning the acquisition, mainly in the fields of town and country planning, architecture and engineering or data processing, of a plan or design selected by a jury. Contracting Authorities that have held a Design Contest shall send a Notice of the results of the contest in accordance with Article 51 and shall be able to prove the date of Despatch.

nodes.name: can-modif
nodes.description: Announcement of Modifications To a Contract during its Term. Contracts and Framework Agreements may be modified without a new Procurement Procedure in accordance with Directive 2014/24/EU.

nodes.name: can-social
nodes.description: Announcement of the results of a call for competition concerning Contracts or Concessions for social and other specific services.

nodes.name: pin-cfc-social
nodes.description: Announcement of intentions of Planned Procurements used as a call for competition concerning Contracts for social and other specific services.
